channel.title: Deciding to start developing rsc again
channel.description:
I used to dev with divine pk 5.0 years ago, (must have been 4+ years :P), but lost interest. I have picked up an interesting for java and runescape classic again and wish to start developing, but would be great if someone could supply me with some good sources with customs/content, other than easyrsc, noobscape, rscd, rsca, or moparclass, because i have all those :P. Feel free to post them here or through a pm, it doesnt matter to me :)
Thanks in advance guys.
